%%%  point vs. extended
 -->

&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;<br>

<table align=center width=90% border=2 cellpadding=3>

<th><font size=+1> <u>DEDUCTIONS FROM OBSERVATIONS</u></font></th>

<tr><td bgcolor="$BBEEEE">

<b>


<!--  %%% ADD! give examples of how determine abundances: Ca, Mg, Fe
%%%  cite Majewski program, gE H-beta, Mg+Fe diag.
%%%  Hard to get light elements: He hard exc v. hot stars;
